## Quick Commands

```bash
# Frontend dev server
cd frontend && npm install && npm run dev

# Backend API server
cd backend && npm install && npm run seed && npm run dev

# Both (from root — use two terminals)
```

See `QUICK_START.md` for full setup instructions.
